author: Mary Papenfuss
title: Ukrainian Americans Protest California Church Talk By Putin Defender Tucker Carlson
description: A megachurch hosted the Kremlin-positive Fox News host — just as horrifying images of murdered civilians in Ukraine emerged.
content: A group of Ukrainian Americans and their supporters gathered outside a conservative Christian megachurch in San Diego County this past weekend to protest a talk inside by Tucker Carlson. The Fox News… [+1788 chars]
